title: Deltaisos for Fedora 13 -> Fedora 14 Beta i386
description:
Deltaisos to generate the entire Fedora 14 Beta i386 install disc set. First apply Fedora-13_14-Beta-i386-DVD.diso to the F13 Final i386 DVD ISO to generate the F14 Beta i386 DVD ISO.  The other deltaisos can then be applied to the new DVD image to generate any of the other new install images (CD and netinst).

Instructions at https://fedoraproject.org/wiki/Delta_ISOs
